Title: Recommendations when publishing a Wasm library
Description: A set of recommendations to make publishing a Javascript library that uses Wasm internally easier for application developers. There are a significant number of use cases and edge cases that we’ll code around as we try and cater to several types of developers: from those who may not know or care about Wasm and the broader JS ecosystem, to more experienced developers who want to optimize every last drop.
